:"2016-12-10T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"多到你唔信⋯識一個銅鑼灣某商廈頂樓連天台佢住晒，拍卡塔lift先上到佢果層，但一年有11個月都唔知塔飛機去左邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">下面十幾層租出去收租，根本好多商廈都係教會，班教友仲咁傻豬貢獻⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"a50b2ed3039be667650c7142409e08848aeb0e93","tid":33071,"uid":62132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>神俾工你返仲要借佢個名收錢<br />\n落地獄啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問下都要落地獄你冇撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔記得幾時有個耶撚都開左個你問我答，次撚次唔同意同屌人落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3e55c40fc38702ad6a048b4820615076fc0b8c","tid":33071,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"其實神父俾咁多錢佢有咩用?<br />\n冇家室, 成世人喺教會做事奉<br />\n(唔守規矩、做衰嘢唔計吖)"},{"pid":"ca78b6b98b1e7e8a3d489099710b195b4f6d5f1f","tid":33071,"uid":27537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:24:59.000Z","msg":"天主教好似冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我識個神父同我講，佢話有靚屋住，但係冇錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車又有"}]}